{"tid":345414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會遊行促放劉霞","createTime":"2017-08-03T05:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T05:22:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b0c4ca0adc4bd4d508202af5e5c215f2815145","tid":345414,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T05:21:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20110228&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20110228%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170803&d=hpBEV%2FeZTgeUkvmWi7ArDP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=91307b27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20110228%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170803&h=2827bce6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20110228&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170803</a><br />\n<br />\n支聯會遊行促放劉霞<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n陳善南攝<br />\n<br />\n【劉曉波逝世】<br />\n昨日是諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波逝世「三七」的日子，支聯會十多名代表手持「釋放劉霞」及「海祭無罪」等標語及橫額，遊行到中聯辦，並進行默哀（圖），抗議內地無理拘捕多名舉辦海邊公祭劉曉波的內地維權人士，而劉曉波的遺孀劉霞更持續受到當局迫害，至今仍然未能自由行動。支聯會對於中共肆意侵犯人權的行為，表達強烈憤慨。"},{"pid":"4e403ac3aa418703df3d80554717ca8c4395b963","tid":345414,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170803/large/03la3p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170803%2Flarge%2F03la3p05.jpg&h=1ea37a5f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}